    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile,</strong> cut&nbsp;the pear<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> into quarters, cutting off the core<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> and chop into&nbsp;wedges</p>",
