    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add </strong>the<strong>&nbsp;</strong>onion to the potato tray&nbsp;with an extra drizzle of oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Place</strong>&nbsp;the tray back in the oven until the end of the next step</p>",
      "order": 4,
