      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, melt 15g <span class=\"text-danger\">(30g)</span>&nbsp;butter and a big pinch of&nbsp;sugar in a pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong>&nbsp;foaming, arrange the pears in a single layer and cook for 2-4 min per side, or until browned and carmelised</p>\r\n<p><strong>Transfer</strong> the pears onto the baking tray, return to the oven and reserve the pan for the next step</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
