          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Wipe </strong>the pan clean and return it to a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>Once </strong>hot</span>, sear the fatty edges of the steaks (using tongs to keep them in place) for 2 min before cooking them for 1 min each side</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
