    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Place</strong> the steaks on top of the onions and cover with cheese and oregano</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pour</strong> any meat juices in the pan over the tray</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return</strong> to the oven and cook for 5-10 min or until the pork steaks are cooked through</p>",
